data.title: Bridal Veil Falls on the Columbia River, Oregon
data.meta_description: Photograph of Bridal Veil Falls on the Columbia River, Oregon, [s.d.]. The waterfall is at center and is a single fall at the top before it splits into two separate falls about halfway down the image. A small body of water is visible in the foreground at center. Many leafy trees can be seen on both sides of the waterfall.
